---
title: Middle Eastern Yoghurt Chicken with Roast Veggie Toss & Feta
description: Combine our popular Souk Market spice blend with yoghurt for a tasty marinade that keeps chicken tender as it bakes. Paired with a roast veggie toss and creamy feta, this colourful meal is a flavour sensation.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/middle-eastern-yoghurt-chicken-8decdb57.jpg
